00:03:24.955 --> 00:03:25.836
And then, I said," you know,

00:03:26.842 --> 00:03:27.862
I think what I really need to be

00:03:27.902 --> 00:03:31.085
doing is I need to track the relationship

00:03:31.604 --> 00:03:35.567
