00:03:40.027 --> 00:03:41.449
creation with the greater and lesser

00:03:41.508 --> 00:03:43.729
luminaries, and the tree of knowledge

00:03:43.770 --> 00:03:45.151
leading to the tree of lives.

00:03:45.211 --> 00:03:49.771
And my Dowd and May Dowd characters, when

00:03:49.931 --> 00:03:51.772
Moshe gave up and said,"

00:03:51.832 --> 00:03:52.913
I can't do this anymore."

00:03:52.933 --> 00:03:53.373
And God said,"

