00:11:33.658 --> 00:11:35.899
And there is no way that Dowd just

00:11:35.958 --> 00:11:39.520
woke up late one afternoon after snoozing

00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:43.602
one off from being drunk on wine and

00:11:43.643 --> 00:11:45.923
got up and staggered to the roof and

00:11:45.964 --> 00:11:47.125
said, I think I want that one.

00:11:48.445 --> 00:11:50.926
And all those things just naturally play

00:11:51.167 --> 00:11:54.067
off from there.

00:11:54.087 --> 00:11:55.469
He had been working up to this for

00:11:55.509 --> 00:11:55.928
some time.

00:11:58.452 --> 00:12:03.635
And so we have a king that had.

