Fifty six aren't actually he was fifty six

00:12:08.600 --> 00:12:09.019
at the time,

00:12:09.059 --> 00:12:10.660
he had forty eight very good years.

00:12:12.782 --> 00:12:13.722
Forty eight very good years,

00:12:13.982 --> 00:12:15.403
that's twice as long as I've been doing

